# 📊 PROMQL — QUERIES IMPORTANTES

## Serviços ativos

```promql
up
```

## CPU %

```promql
100 - (avg by(instance)(rate(node_cpu_seconds_total{mode='idle'}[5m])) * 100)
```

## Memória %

```promql
(1 - (node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes/node_memory_MemTotal_bytes)) * 100
```

## Disco %

```promql
(1-(node_filesystem_avail_bytes{mountpoint='/'}/node_filesystem_size_bytes{mountpoint='/'})) * 100
```

## Requisições por segundo

```promql
sum(rate(lab_http_requests_total[5m]))
```

## Taxa de erro 5xx

```promql
sum(rate(lab_http_requests_total{status=~'5..'}[5m])) / sum(rate(lab_http_requests_total[5m])) * 100
```

## Latência P95

```promql
histogram_quantile(0.95, rate(lab_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m]))
```

